==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Evanescence
<hw>Ev`a*nes"cence</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act or
state of vanishing away; disappearance; <as>as, the <ex>evanescence</ex>
of vapor, of a dream, of earthly plans or hopes</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Rambler.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Evanescent</ent>⟦br⟧
